Date: Fri, 10 May 2019 10:59:58 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: dt: add support for fsl-imx8qxp-tqma8xqp-mbpa8xx

Signed-off-by: Markus Niebel <Markus.Niebel@tq-group.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/Makefile        |   1 +
 .../fsl-imx8qxp-tqma8xqp-mbpa8xx.dts          |  24 +++
 .../boot/dts/freescale/mbpa8xx-common.dtsi    | 157 ++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 182 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8qxp-tqma8xqp-mbpa8xx.dts
